#, fuzzy
msgid "Westin Guard"
msgstr "Westin"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:155
msgid ""
"Commander!  I took your message to the council, and your deeds have pleased "
"them.  Are the undead finally gone from our lands?"
msgstr ""
"Comandante! Ho portato il vostro messaggio al consiglio, e le vostre azioni "
"lo hanno soddisfatto. Siete finalmente riusciti a scacciare i non-morti "
"dalle nostre terre?"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:159
msgid ""
"The undead are gone!  Perhaps now there will be peace for a time in Westin.  "
"You have our thanks Lady Ethiliel."
msgstr ""
"I non-morti sono andati! Forse avremo pace per qualche tempo a Westin. Avete "
"i nostri ringraziamenti, Lady Ethiliel."

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Though the undead are vanquished, they have brought us much sorrow.  Deoran, "
"your people have restored their honor.  Let us part in peace."
msgstr ""
"Anche se i non-morti sono stati sterminati, ci hanno portato molto dolore. "
"Deoran, il tuo popolo ha restaurato il suo onore ai nostri occhi. "
"Dividiamoci in pace."

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:167
msgid ""
"Indeed.  Neither the bandits nor the undead will trouble us for some time.  "
"We will tend our wounds and you yours."
msgstr ""
"Daccordo. Ne i banditi, ne i non-morti ci causeranno guai per qualche tempo. "
"baderemo alle nostre ferite, così come voi baderete alle vostre."

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:171
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:180
msgid "Help!"
msgstr "Aiuto!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:190
msgid "Poor Farmer"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:197
msgid "You must pay for killing Mebrin!"
msgstr "Pagherai per aver ucciso Mebrin!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:201
msgid "I am just a farmer!  What did I do?!"
msgstr "Sono solo un contadino! Cosa ho fatto?!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:205
msgid ""
"What did you do?!  Your people kidnapped and murdered our greatest leader!  "
"And now you will pay!"
msgstr ""
"Cosa hai fatto?! Il tuo popolo ha rapito ed ucciso il nostro più grande "
"saggio! Ed ora tu pagherai!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:226
msgid "He just killed that innocent farmer!  We must stop him!"
msgstr "Ha appena ucciso quel contadino innocente! Dobbiamo fermarlo!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Stop Ithelden!  I have traveled with these humans, and they are not the ones "
"who harmed Mebrin.  They are our allies!"
msgstr ""
"Fermati Ithelden! Ho viaggiato con questi umani, e non sono coloro che hanno "
"fatto del male a Mebrin. Sono nostri alleati!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:234
msgid ""
"You too Ethiliel?  All these menfolk are the same!  They fell trees to till "
"the earth; now they have felled our leader!  We cannot brook such deeds!  "
"You will die with them!"
msgstr ""
"Anche tu, Ethiliel? Tutti gli uomini sono gli stessi! così come tagliano gli "
"alberi per preparare la terra, ora eliminano i nostri saggi! Non possiamo "
"permetter loro di agire impuniti! Morirai con loro!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:240
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:241
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:242
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:243
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:244
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:245
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:246
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:295
msgid "Disciple of Mebrin"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:251
msgid "Keep the enraged elves from sacking Westin"
msgstr "Trattieni gli elfi infuriati dal saccheggiare Westin"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:308
msgid "For every one of us you strike down, more will rise!"
msgstr "Per ognuno di noi che cade, altri combatteranno!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:319
msgid ""
"We won't be able to hold them off for long.  I should go reason with them!  "
"They won't dare attack me."
msgstr ""
"Non saremo in grado di tenerli a distanza a lungo. Devo indurli alla "
"ragione! Non oseranno attaccarmi!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:323
msgid ""
"Are you sure that the elves will greet you any more kindly than they have "
"met us?  After all, you did lead us into the forests..."
msgstr ""
"Sei certa che gli elfi ti accoglieranno più calorosamente di come hanno "
"accolto noi? Dopotutto ci hai guidati tu nella foresta..."

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:327
msgid "Perhaps not, but it is your only hope.  I must reach Ithelden!"
msgstr "Forse no, ma è la nostra unica speranza. Devo raggiungere Ithelden!"

#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/8a.Vengeance.cfg:335
msgid "Bring Ethiliel to a parlay with Ithelden"
msgstr "Porta Ethiliel a Discutere con Ithelden"

